snippet.title: Alan Wake 2 - Official Saga Anderson Gameplay Trailer | Xbox Partner Preview
snippet.description: Check out some extended, and very creepy, gameplay of Alan Wake 2's new character, Saga Anderson. Alan Wake 2 is the upcoming anticipated sequel from Remedy Studios, and will release on October 27, 2023. Revealed during the Xbox Partner Preview on http://www.youtube.com/xbox
